0.4.1 2026-02-15
    - Removed no longer needed workaround for export of KWICs from licensed texts with Firefox (kupietz)

0.4.0 2026-02-14
    - Upgraded Docker Java to 25.
    - Upgraded target Java to 21.
    - Fix export of KWICs from licensed texts with Firefox and Safari (kupietz).
    - Added support for randomizing page order in export (resolves #182) (kupietz).

