      (closes #161)(diewald)
    - Fix GitLab CI pipeline (kupietz)
    - Fixed hard-coded export limit in template (kupietz)
    - Added test for for maxHitC (diewald)
    - Upgrade Jersey to 4.0.2 (dependabot)
    - Upgrade other dependencies (dependabot)

